snippet.description:
▶Nepali Superchat: https://cr8.rs/@cr7-horaa

Hello, welcome to my live stream and channel.
If you like the stream, press like, share with your friends and subscribe to the channel. Also make sure to press the notifications button.
____________________________________________________

   ▶Instagram- https://www.instagram.com/cr7horaaaa/
   ▶Facebook- https://www.facebook.com/CR7-horaa-106165508386509
Follow on TikTok: https://vt.tiktok.com/ZSNweKMN4/
   ▶Discord- https://discord.gg/QSwfPktSCf
____________________________________________________

Owner of HORAA eSports
   ▶ On instagram: https://www.instagram.com/horaaesports/
   ▶On youtube: https://www.youtube.com/@HoraaEsportsOfficial

____________________________________________________

🏆 GRAND FINALS DAY 2 | AUGUST 2

ESPORTS WORLD CUP ma 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ultimate stage ma pugheko cha – the Grand Finals Day 2 begins today in Riyadh! After days of fierce competition, the top 16 teams in the world have earned their place to fight for glory, legacy, and the lion’s share of the $3,000,000 prize pool.

After days of fierce competition, globe ko top 16 PUBG MOBILE teams le final stage ma afno place secure garisakeka chan - chasing glory, legacy, and a share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. This is the moment every team has been grinding for and one day is already behind. The best from the Group Stage and the survivors of the Survival Stage now go head-to-head in the most intense showdown of the year. Three days, SMASH RULE, and one champion.

The journey reaches a new height —kinaki kebal euta team le trophy uthaune cha and and etch their name into PUBG MOBILE history. Let the Grand Finals Day 2 begin.

🔥SMASH RULE le kasari kaam garcha?
Grand Finals ko Day 2 pachi match point threshold lai #1 rank ma raheko team ko points +10 ma set garine cha. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals - winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn’t bring the championship. If kunai pani teams le Match 18 samma ma SMASH RULE bata title secure garena bhane the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

🔥 Why You Can’t Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
The top 16 teams on one stage — no second chances!
Every match counts in the race for the championship!
Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
Explosive SMASH RULE format — pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!

📅 TOURNAMENT SCHEDULE
Group Stage: July 25–27
Survival Stage: July 29–30
Grand Finals: August 1–3

Try PUBG MOBILE now: https://pubgmobile.live/2025PMWC

💰 Total Prize Pool: $3,000,000
📍 Venue: Boulevard Riyadh City, Saudi Arabia


🏆 GRAND FINALS TEAMS:

Alter Ego Ares  
Alpha Gaming

IDA Esports

From Director James Cameron, watch the trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash.
Experience the film only in theaters December 19.

With “Avatar: Fire and Ash,” James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na’vi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na’vi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Britain Dalton, Trinity Bliss, Jack Champion, Bailey Bass and Kate Winslet.

snippet.title: [NP] 2025 PMWC at EWC Grand Finals D3 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
ESPORTS WORLD CUP ma 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ko epic conclusion ko lagi stage set cha! After weeks of breath-taking competition, today marks the final day of the Grand Finals in Riyadh, where one team will rise above the rest to claim the crown and secure their place in PUBG MOBILE history.

This is it — EWC ma 2025 PMWC ko last matches. World ko best 16 teams have given everything, but only one will lift the trophy and take home the lion’s share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. Harek rotation, harek zone ra harek elimination le aja pura championship ko outcome change garna sakcha kinaki, now a team can win with SMASH RULE.

Group stage ra Survival Stage ko unforgettable journey pachi, today we crown the champion of 2025 PMWC at EWC.

🔥SMASH RULE le kasari kaam garcha?
Grand Finals ko Day 2 pachi match point threshold lai #1 rank ma raheko team ko points +10 ma set garine cha. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals - winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn’t bring the championship. If kunai pani teams le Match 18 samma ma SMASH RULE bata title secure garena bhane the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

🔥 Why You Can’t Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
- The top 16 teams on one stage — no second chances!
- Every match counts in the race for the championship!
- Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
- Explosive SMASH RULE format — pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!

📅 TOURNAMENT SCHEDULE
Group Stage: July 25–27
Survival Stage: July 29–30
Grand Finals: August 1–3

Try PUBG MOBILE now: https://pubgmobile.live/2025PMWC

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

The biggest love song of the year #Pardesiya, song out now!

🎧 Listen Now On:

➟ Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/0q84FggW57NXGtLHoetS0Y?si=69de460ee14e4e86

#ParamSundari releasing in cinemas worldwide on 29th August 2025.

🎧 Song Credits :

🎶 Music : Sachin-Jigar 
🎤 Singer : Sonu Nigam  Krishnakali Saha & Sachin-Jigar
➟ Lyrics : Amitabh Bhattacharya

➟ Mixed & Mastered : Eric Pillai @ FSOB
➟ Assistant mix Engineer - Michael Edwin Pillai

🎬 Video Credits

Maddock Films presents #ParamSundari In cinemas on 29th August 2025

➟ Cast: Sidharth Malhotra and Janhvi Kapoor 
➟ Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
➟ Directed By: Tushar Jalota
➟ Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota & Poonam Shivdasani
➟ Director Of Photography : Santhanakrishnan
➟ Story by: Gaurav Mishra, Aarsh Vora, Tushar Jalota
➟ Screenplay and Dialogues: Aarsh Vora, Tushar Jalota
➟ Music By: Sachin-Jigar
➟ Background Score: Sachin-Jigar
➟ Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya 
➟ Additional Dialogues: Gaurav Mishra
➟ Costume Designer : Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
➟ Director Of Choreography: Brinda Gopal
➟ Publicity Design: Himanshu & Rahul Nanda (H-One)

Lyrics:

Pardesiya..
Hai tere pyar mein jab se
Jhankaar si..
Hai dil ke taar mein tab se

Tum ho mere jaanta hun magar
Pohchaauñ tum tak ye kaise khabar

Kab se hun main ummeed meiñ
Hai ankaha jo sun lo agar

Pardesiya..
Mila hai tu mujhe jab se

Maiñ qaid huñ
Tere bhi pyar mein tab se ..

Pardesiya haiñ teri batiyoñ ne 
Kiya pareshan pardesiya..

Pardesiya haiñ teri ankhiyoñ ke
Dil pe nishaan pardesiya..
 
Chhoo ke laboñ se jaise
Jaadu hi kar diya
Saavan ne morni ko
Qaabu mein kar liya

Hum dono ki juda theeñ hastiyaañ
Hoñ kinara bin jaise kashtiyaañ

Aasaan ho aage safar
Tum saath mera chun lo agar

Pardesiya.. 

#SonuNigam #SidharthMalhotra #JanhviKapoor

ESPORTS WORLD CUP ma 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ko epic conclusion ko lagi stage set cha! After weeks of breath-taking competition, today marks the final day of the Grand Finals in Riyadh, where one team will rise above the rest to claim the crown and secure their place in PUBG MOBILE history.

This is it — EWC ma 2025 PMWC ko last matches. World ko best 16 teams have given everything, but only one will lift the trophy and take home the lion’s share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. Harek rotation, harek zone ra harek elimination le aja pura championship ko outcome change garna sakcha kinaki, now a team can win with SMASH RULE.

Group stage ra Survival Stage ko unforgettable journey pachi, today we crown the champion of 2025 PMWC at EWC.

🔥SMASH RULE le kasari kaam garcha?
Grand Finals ko Day 2 pachi match point threshold lai #1 rank ma raheko team ko points +10 ma set garine cha. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals - winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn’t bring the championship. If kunai pani teams le Match 18 samma ma SMASH RULE bata title secure garena bhane the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

🔥 Why You Can’t Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
The top 16 teams on one stage — no second chances!
Every match counts in the race for the championship!
Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
Explosive SMASH RULE format — pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!

📅 TOURNAMENT SCHEDULE
Group Stage: July 25–27
Survival Stage: July 29–30
Grand Finals: August 1–3

Try PUBG MOBILE now: https://pubgmobile.live/2025PMWC

💰 Total Prize Pool: $3,000,000
📍 Venue: Boulevard Riyadh City, Saudi Arabia

snippet.title: बिहे गरी ल्याउ राम PAURANIKE NEW TEEJ SONG 2082 BIHE GARI LYAU RAM  4K TEEJ VIDEO
snippet.description:
Hari Devi Koirala Presents:-बिहे गरी ल्याउ राम BIHE GARI LYAU RAM II HARI DEVI KOIRALA II PAURANIKE NEW TEEJ SONG 2082 स्वर,शब्द,लय हरिदेबी कोइराला  छायाङकन प्रदिप कुमार नापित   अंकित खैजु

snippet.title: The Conjuring: Last Rites | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover why this case ended it all. #TheConjuring: Last Rites - Only in Theaters September 5.

From New Line Cinema comes the ninth entry in the more than $2 billion theatrical Conjuring universe, The Conjuring: Last Rites, directed by franchise veteran Michael Chaves and produced by franchise architects James Wan and Peter Safran.

The Conjuring: Last Rites delivers another thrilling chapter of the iconic Conjuring cinematic universe, based on real events.  Vera Farmiga and Patrick Wilson reunite for one last case as renowned, real-life paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren in a powerful and spine-chilling addition to the global box office-breaking franchise.

Farmiga and Wilson star alongside Mia Tomlinson and Ben Hardy, who portray Ed and Lorraine’s daughter Judy Warren and her boyfriend, Tony Spera, as well as Steve Coulter returning as Father Gordon, Rebecca Calder, Elliot Cowan, Kíla Lord Cassidy, Beau Gadsdon, John Brotherton and Shannon Kook.

Chaves directs from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing and David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, story by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick & James Wan, based on characters created by Chad Hayes & Carey W. Hayes.  The executive producers are Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Hans Ritter, David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, Natalia Safran, John Rickard and Michael Chaves.

Chaves is joined behind the camera by his creative team, including director of photography Eli Born, production designer John Frankish, editors Elliot Greenberg and Gregory Plotkin, visual effects supervisor Scott Edelstein, visual effects producer Eric Bruneau and costume designer Graham Churchyard, with casting by Rose Wicksteed and Sophie Kingston-Smith.  The music supervisor is Ian Broucek and the music is by composer Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents The Safran Company / An Atomic Monster Production, The Conjuring: Last Rites.  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and will be only in theaters and IMAX® in North America on September 5, 2025, and internationally beginning 3 September 2025.

snippet.description:
#ranichatterjee #sanjanapandey #prashantsingh #ladomadhesiya #vidhyasingh #manjulthakur #omjha #arbindtiwari #bhojpurimovie#bhojpuri  #saasbahuchaliswarglok #swarlok #trending

IVY ENTERTAINMENT PRESENTS IN ASSOCIATION WITH SHREE AADYA ENTERTAINMENT

फ़िल्म – सास बहू चली स्वर्ग लोक  (भोजपुरी फिल्म )
कलाकार - रानी  चटर्जी , संजना  पांडेय  ,लाडो मधेसिया ,प्रशांत  सिंह  , विद्या  सिंह , गोपाल  चव्हाण  , अलोक  कुमार , पार्थ  मिश्रा  ,राजेश  तोमर , नविन  चंद्रा, प्रीति राज , सोनाली मिश्रा

कांसेप्ट - संदीप सिंह
पटकथा - मंजुल ठाकुर , अरविन्द तिवारी
कथा , व संवाद - अरविन्द तिवारी
संगीतकार- ओम झा
छायांकन - सुनील  आहेर

 म्यूजिक,सॅटॅलाइट और डिजिटल पार्टनर - B4U भोजपुरी


B4U क्रिएटिव टीम – 
मारुद शर्मा, नेहा उपाध्याय, विशाल यादव , निशी राय

snippet.title: [Official Trailer] REVAMP THE UNDEAD STORY
snippet.description:
ปัณณ์ (เปรม-วรุศ) ชายหนุ่มเจ้าของร้านขายวัตถุโบราณได้รับการว่าจ้างจากเพื่อนสนิทให้ไปซ่อมภาพวาด แต่ปัณณ์กลับถูกเศษกระจกบาดจนเลือดไปเปื้อนกับภาพเขียนเข้าโดยไม่ตั้งใจ ทำให้ รามิล (บุ๋น-นพณัฐ) ทายาทคนสุดท้ายของตระกูลแวมไพร์ที่ถูกผนึกไว้ในภาพวาดมากกว่าร้อยปีฟื้นขึ้นมา ทว่ารามิลกลับไร้พลังและกำลังถูกกลุ่ม “ฮันเตอร์” นักล่าแวมไพร์ตามล่า ปัณณ์จึงจำเป็นต้องช่วยเหลือรามิลให้พลังของเขาฟื้นคืน ด้วยการออกตามหาบริวารตนอื่นๆ จนทำให้ความสัมพันธ์ของทั้งคู่ค่อยๆ พัฒนาขึ้น
 การเดินทางของปัณณ์ รามิล และกลุ่มฮันเตอร์ที่กำลังตามล่าครั้งนี้จะเป็นยังไง และความสัมพันธ์ระหว่างมนุษย์กับแวมไพร์จะสามารถรักกันได้ไหม ติดตามได้ใน “REVAMP THE UNDEAD STORY” ทุกวันเสาร์ เวลา 20:30 น. ทางช่อง GMM25 และดูออนไลน์ เวลา 21:30 น. บนแอป iQIYI และเว็บ iQ.com ที่เดียวเท่านั้น เริ่มตอนแรก 23 สิงหาคมนี้

กำกับซีรีส์ : ศิวัจน์ สวัสดิ์มณีกุล

รายชื่อนักแสดง
บุ๋น นพณัฐ กันทะชัย   รับบท  รามิล
เปรม วรุศ ชวลิตรุจิวงษ์   รับบท  ปัณณ์
มาร์ค จิรันธนิน ตรัยรัตนยนต์  รับบท  เมธัส
บาร์โค้ด ตฤณสิษฐ์ อิสระพงศ์พร  รับบท  คีอาร์
อั๋น ณภัทร​ พัชรชวลิต   รับบท  เมฆิณ
เค เลิศสิทธิชัย            รับบท  เจตต์
กระปุก พลอยนิรา หิรัญทวีศิลป์       รับบท  เอลีส์
เอเจ ชยพล จุฑามาศ    รับบท  พอล
เจเจ ชยกร จุฑามาศ    รับบท  แคสเตอร์
แสตมป์ พนัชษ์กรณ์ ฤกษ์ศิริอารี รับบท  ปกป้อง
#RevampSeries

snippet.title: लालू जी की LOVE Story | Official Trailer | Yash Kumarr, Mahima Gupta | New Bhojpuri Movie 2025
snippet.description:
🎬 Official Trailer – "लालू जी की LOVE Story" | A Bhojpuri Romantic Drama | Yash Kumarr & Mahima Gupta

तन्वी मल्टीमीडिया प्रस्तुत करती है 2025 की सबसे दिलचस्प प्रेम कहानी – "लालू जी की LOVE Story", जिसमें रोमांस है, कॉमेडी है और परिवार का प्यारा तड़का।

स्टार कास्ट: यश कुमार, महिमा गुप्ता, अनुप अरोरा, भानु पांडे, श्रद्धा नवल, राधे कुमार, अनु पांडे, श्रवण तिवारी, दिव्या शर्मा, कविता पांडे

🎥 फिल्म क्रेडिट्स:
◾तन्वी मल्टीमीडिया 
◾निर्माता - दीपक शाह 
◾निर्देशक - सुजीत वर्मा 
◾संगीत - साजन मिश्रा व मुन्ना दुबे 
◾गीत - आशुतोष तिवारी,राजेश मिश्रा 
◾गायक - विजय चौहान,प्रियंका सिंह,सिंगधा सरकार,खुशबू जैन 
◾संवाद व पाठकथा - राकेश त्रिपाठी 
◾कथा - यश कुमार 
◾छायंकन - समीर जहांगीर सैयद
◾संकलन - गुरजेंट सिंह
◾नूत्य - प्रवीण शेलार
◾कार्यकारी निर्माता - शैलेंद्र सिंह
◾कला - अवधेश राय
◾ड्रेस डिज़ायनर - नानू फ़ैशन(विद्या-विष्णु)
◾प्रचारक - रंजन शिन्हा 
◾पब्लिसिट डिज़ाइनर - सूरज गिरी
◾रूप सज्जा - ख़लील रहमान
◾रेकोडिस्ट - अशोक यादव
◾डी आई - इन्द्रजीत यादव
◾पोस्ट प्रडक्शन - आई फ़ोकस स्टूडीओ(विजय दिनेश) व वोट प्रोडक्शन

👉 ये ट्रेलर देखें और जानें क्या है लालू जी की लव स्टोरी में ख़ास।
🎧 बेहतरीन संगीत, ज़बरदस्त डायलॉग्स और मस्त कहानी।

📢 अब ट्रेंडिंग में लाने के लिए वीडियो को लाइक करें, शेयर करें और कमेंट ज़रूर करें!

💑 कहानी:
“लालू जी की LOVE Story” एक साधारण लेकिन बेहद दिलचस्प युवक लालू की कहानी है, जो अपने सीधेपन, मासूमियत और बेइंतहा प्यार के चलते एक अनोखी प्रेम यात्रा पर निकल पड़ता है। यह सिर्फ लव स्टोरी नहीं, बल्कि एक भावनात्मक rollercoaster है जिसमें कॉमेडी, ड्रामा और रिश्तों की गहराई है।

🌟 मुख्य भूमिकाओं में:
◾ Yash Kumarr – एक बार फिर अपने अनोखे अंदाज़ में
◾ Mahima Gupta – शानदार अदायगी के साथ
उनकी ऑनस्क्रीन केमिस्ट्री इस फिल्म का प्रमुख आकर्षण है।

snippet.title: [EN] 2025 PMWC at EWC Grand Finals D3 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
🏆 GRAND FINALS DAY 3 | AUGUST 3

The stage is set for the epic conclusion of the 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP! After weeks of breath taking competition, today marks the final day of the Grand Finals in Riyadh, where one team will rise above the rest to claim the crown and secure their place in PUBG MOBILE history.

This is it — the last matches of 2025 PMWC at EWC. The world’s best 16 teams have given everything, but only one will lift the trophy and take home the lion’s share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. Every rotation, every zone, and every elimination today could change the outcome of the entire championship because, now a team can win with SMASH RULE.

After an unforgettable journey through the Group Stage and the Survival Stage, today we crown the champion of 2025 PMWC at EWC.

🔥 How does SMASH RULE work? 
On the last day of the 2025 PMWC Grand Finals, we have the Match Point Threshold! In Overall Ranking after 12th match, #1 ranked team’s points +10. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy—winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn’t bring the championship. If no team secures the title via SMASH Rule by Match 18, the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

🔥 Why You Can’t Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
- The top 16 teams on one stage — no second chances!
- Every match counts in the race for the championship!
- Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
- Explosive SMASH RULE format — pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!


📅 TOURNAMENT SCHEDULE
Group Stage: July 25–27
Survival Stage: July 29–30
Grand Finals: August 1–3

Try PUBG MOBILE now: https://pubgmobile.live/2025PMWC

💰 Total Prize Pool: $3,000,000
📍 Venue: Boulevard Riyadh City, Saudi Arabia

बैंस भरियो छोटो भो जामा
बरबराउन लाईछु रे निद्रामा

ऐना अघी हाँस्छु मुख छेकेर
आफ्नै जिउ को बनावट देखेर 

प्रत्येक दिन जिन्दगी भरिका
फोनमै हुन्चन् बात अनेक थरीका

लाउन मन्छ जिन्दगी भरी
उनकै नामको सिन्दुर र तिलहरी

भेटेँ उनलाई जिन्दगी अर्थ भो
पानी नखाई बसेको बर्तको 


भन ए संगी भन
पोहोरको तिजमा नाच्न पाईन खुलेर 
यसपाली तिजमा चोरी भयो मन

snippet.title: Mutu Mai Basecha - Female Version (Alternate/Extended) Bashiruddin Miyan
snippet.description:
Mutu Mae Basecha - Female Version (Alternate/Extended) Bashiruddin Miyan

🎶 Mutu Mai Basechha (Female Version Cover) 🎶

Originally performed by Brijesh Shrestha/Samikshya Adhikari, this is my heartfelt female interpretation of the beautiful song Mutu Mai Basechha. I've added some extra verses to express a different emotional perspective—one that reflects a softer, more intimate side of the story.

✨ This version is not just a cover—it's a reimagined expression of love, pain, and longing from a female voice. I hope you connect with this rendition just as deeply as I did while creating it.

🎧 Original Song Credits:
Title: Mutu Mai Basechha
Original Artist: Brijesh Shrestha & Samiksha Adhikari
Composer & Lyricist: Brijesh Shrestha /Kusum Nepal

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Lyrics :-

Pokhara, ghumauna laijane ko chha ra

Dhangadhi, nadulau mayale man badhi

Baisalu manle ke sochchha sohchha 
Mayakai sathma ramauna khojchha

Ma pani timrai timi ni merai
Lekheko vanda paidaina dherai

Ainama herchhu ramri nai lauchha
Magar soltyle jiskaudai aauchha

Ki chaine rupa ki chaine dhana
Herdainan kohi kasto chha mana

Hami ni sangai Pokhara jamla
Lekhside tira chatpate khamla

Umermai honi ramailo garni
Yatti kura ni samjhauna parni

sathiko boyfriend majjako raichha
Sang sangai Mustang ghumna lai gaichha

Dhan paisa bhuiko dhulo ho sathi
Manako khusi thulo ho sathi

Aakhaima gajal galaima dimple
Aafu ta manchhe sojhi ra simple

Man parchha timro jiskine bani
Ma raja timro timi hau rani

Aafno ta kohi chhaina kar launi
Aruko jodi dekhda rahar launi

Daya ra baya nagare feri
Timi ta kebal meri hau meri

Bor lagyo katai jam maya vanos
Chiso tato kehi kham maya vanos

Chhinmai risauni chhinmai furkini
Anekau chhan ke timra ghurkini

Aaja ni kaam chha voli ni kaam chha
Yahi bhanda bhandai jindagi janchha

Sarkari hoina jagir chha niji
timi ni bg ma pani bg
-------------------------------------
पोखरा, घुमाउन लैजाने कोछ र 
धनगढी, नडुलाउ मायाले मन बढी

बैसालु मनले के सोच्छ सोच्छ 
मायाकै साथमा रमाउन खोज्छ

म पनि तिम्रै तिमि नि मेरै
लेखेको भन्दा पाईदैन धेरै 

ऐनामा हेर्छु राम्री नै लाउछ
मगर सोल्टीले जिस्काउदै आउछ

कि चाहिने रुप कि चाहिने धन 
हेर्दैनन कोहि कस्तो छ मन 

हामी नि संगै पोखरा जाम्ला
लेखसाईड तिर चटपटे खाम्ला

उमेरमै होनि रमाइलो गर्नी
यत्ती कुरानी सम्झाउन पर्नी

साथीको ब्वाईफ्रेन्ड मज्जाको रैछ
संग संगै मुस्ताङ घुम्नलाई गैछ

धन पैसा भुईको धुलो हो साथी
मनको खुसी ठुलो हो साथी

आखैमा गाजल गालैमा डिम्पल 
आफू त मान्छे सोझि र सिम्पल 

मन पर्छ तिम्रो जिस्किने बानी
म राजा तिम्रो तिमी हौ रानी 

आफ्नो त कोहि छैन कर लाउनी
अरुको जोडी देख्दा रहर लाउनी 

दायाँ र बायाँ नगरे फेरि
तिमी त केवल मेरी हौ मेरी

बोर लाग्यो कतै जाम माया भनोस
चिसो तातो केही खाम माया भनोस

छिनमै रिसाउनी छिनमै फुर्किनी 
अनेकौ छनके तिम्रा घुर्किनी 

आज नि काम छ भोलि नि काम छ
यहि भन्दा भन्दै जिन्दगी जान्छ

सरकारी होईन जागिर छ निजि
तिमी नि बिजि म पनि बिजि

All Rights Reserved

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Samir Shrestha - Auna Najeeka ( Ahbhagi )  ( Official Lyrical Video )
snippet.description:
“Aauna Naajeka” is a song for anyone who’s ever felt lost, tired, or questioned their path. It speaks to the quiet struggles we often carry alone—the heartbreaks, the disappointments, the moments when everything feels heavy. But more than anything, it’s a reminder that even when life feels uncertain, we are not alone. There is always a light, always a presence—whether you call it God, love, or something greater—that holds us through it all. This song is a gentle embrace, a message of hope, and a call to keep believing, even when it’s hard.

Written, composed, and performed by Samir Shrestha
